  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors fully assessed at high rigor; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and global sensitivity analysis are performed and linked. All achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Decision: Accepted.",
