      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three grids (5.2M, 12.1M, 28.4M cells). Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index < 2.1% on finest grid. Temporal convergence confirmed with CFL < 0.8. All metrics below required threshold for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
