      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/model-inputs-mrl5",
      "rationale": "All 14 model input parameters characterized with probability distributions from measurement data. Monte Carlo sampling (N=2000, Latin hypercube) propagated through full CFD model. Sobol first-order and total-order indices computed for all inputs. Top three influential inputs (inlet flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity) account for 87% of output variance. Input uncertainty report UI-COU2-001 archived."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
