      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/test-samples-mrl5",
      "rationale": "Five distinct operating conditions tested with n=3 experimental replicates per condition (15 total runs). Sample size justified by power analysis (power=0.85, alpha=0.05) for detecting 10% hemolysis difference. Pump geometry manufactured to ISO 2768 tolerances; dimensional inspection records archived. Batch-to-batch fluid variability characterized and included in UQ."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
